Product name: Italian Leather Tote Bag with YKK Zipper Option, Italian Leather Tote , Leather Purse, Leather Laptop Bag, Leather Shoulder Bag, Leather Bag
Description:
Italian Leather Tote Bag made from supple, milled Italian Leather, with front pocket-available with YKK Zipper
Our Black Leather Tote Bag, with a front pocket, is the perfect companion for your everyday adventures. Whether your on or off the subway, or a day out shopping or simply meeting friends for coffee, this versatile bag will look good with any outfit and will meet all your needs....let the adventures start here......
The Bag
Our black Italian leather tote has a front pocket and two internal pockets. It has a D ring attached inside to keep your keys separate and gives you easy access to them. This leather tote is big enough to carry a 13" laptop, books, phone, magazines, keys, purse and even lunch. The tote in the picture is shown in black and it is also available in whisky and light tan. This bag is now available with a YKK Brass Zipper
A Sign of Quality
Each leather tote bag is expertly crafted using only the best materials to give beauty and quality, as well as strength and durability you can rely on. Every bag is precisely hand cut, the edges of the bag and straps are bevelled and edge-coated to give a high standard finish and feels comfortable in the hand
***We only use the best materials…..
The leather….Italian Milled Vegetable Tanned Leather
Straps….Italian Smooth Vegetable Tanned Leather
Stitch-Machine and Hand-stiched using a Waxed Polyester Thread
Zipper-YKK Brass Zipper
Hardware….Solid Brass
Packaging….Cotton Dust Bag
Delivery….Tracked from the UK
Our Leather
We source our leather from the Tuscany region of Italy renowned for some of the best leathers in the world. The leather used for this tote is a vegetable tanned leather that has gone through a milling process-which gives a beautiful rich texture- as the fibres are loosened to make it soft, but retain structure. We also use a smooth veg tan leather for the straps, when combined with the milled leather, produce bags with an unmistakeable look and feel of quality.

Product name: Vintage Austrian enamel bangle bracelet, blue with handpainted white and golden floral decor, traditional folk art, Trachtenschmuck
Description:
Here is a beautiful Austrian enamel bangle I recently discovered at a Munich flea market. Beautifully handpainted golden floral designs on a white enamel base.
This is what is called Trachtenschmuck, traditional Austrian jewelry worn with a dirndl to occasions, traditional festivities, etc. 
I love accessorizing colorful summery dresses, embroidered blouses with my Austrian folk art bangles, they go with so many things!
I dated the bracelet as made in the 80s... but it could be older as well. At the flea market I picked up a couple of bracelets as you can see on the last photo, some of them have adhesives on the inside, some a handwritten "Austria", the label is still there on the inside of the bracelet in this case.
The bangle is in good vintage condition with no chips in the enamel and all painted details well preserved.
Measurements:
diameter 2.5 in / 6,3 cm, measured on the inside. It's a regular women's size.
The bangles pictured in the last image all come in two sizes, the 4 stacked bangles on the right are women's size, the two on the left kids sizes. (That said, I have rather slim hands and can just about slip the kids sizes over my hands to give you an idea...) 
Please see further listings for details on the other bangles, or just convo me!
Shipping:
I'm happy to ship anywhere in the world, as well as combine shipping for two or more items – please contact me for shipping rates if you don't see your country. 
For environmental reasons, I try to re-use packaging material whenever possible.

Product name: Recycled Lighthouse suncatcher, aqua lighthouse ornament, window art
Description:
This aqua lighthouse suncatcher is made by hand from 100% post-consumer bottle glass at our non-profit community recycling center. Hang it in your window and let the sunlight sparkle through! About 4 1/4 inches in diameter, with hemp hanging cord.
Glass bottles come in to our recycling plant from community drop-offs and curbside. We then hand-select and divert specific bottles to the "hot shop" to be melted down and made into sparkling, colorful suncatchers. 
All suncatchers are strung with a hemp cord and a tag explaining it was made from 100% post-consumer bottles at a non-profit facility.
Small suncatchers are ~3 1/4 In. in diameter, and large suncatchers are ~4 1/4 in. in diameter. They can be easily hung with a suction cup (not provided) in a window.
Green suncatchers are made from 100% green bottles, primarily beer bottles, but some wine and liquor bottles also. Amber suncatchers are made from a mixture of brown beer bottles and clear bottles. Blue suncatchers are made from a mixture of blue beer and wine bottles and clear bottles. Aqua suncatchers are made from 100% clear bottles to which colorants are added to attain the aqua color.
Because each suncatcher is individually made by hand, there will be slight variations in size, bubbles, rim thickness, and coloration.
The Glass reFactory is part of Adams Brown Recycling, which provides diverse recycling services in rural Adams & Brown counties, Ohio. As part of our Community Action Program, our mission is to meet the needs of, and help, low-income residents in our area. Adams Brown Recycling and The Glass reFactory provide local jobs, help to put money in residents' pockets through the purchase of recyclables, raises recycling & solid waste awareness of the public through assertive educational activities, and is a  unique social enterprise that fosters local pride.

Product name: Focus 5 Copper Spinning Top
Description:
Precisely machined and hand assembled the Focus 5 Copper is a great spinner.  It consistently performs better than the brass versions of the Focus 5.  We engineered this top to have some of the longest spin times around.  After making the copper body in our CNC (Computer Numerically Controlled) lathe we install and secure a ceramic ball in the tip.  This ball is the secret to our long spin times which average 2-3 minutes.  Our longest spin so far is 5:07!  It also means your nice new top isn't wrecked the first time it falls on the floor.

Once the item is added to your cart, please leave the following in the NOTES TO SELLER section:
- Napkin Color
- Ink Color
- Customization Information

- Any other information we need to know 
PROOFS
We send proofs for all personalized items within 24 business hours. This digital proof is sent to you via Etsy conversation. 3 complimentary proofs will be sent to ensure you are fully in love with the design. Additional proofs will cost 5. 
Your order is held until we hear back from you with approval that all spelling and punctuation is correct. Please note that are orders are immediately placed into production once we receive your approval, and changes cannot be made. A delay in approving your proof WILL delay the production time stated below. 
PRODUCTION TIME
Napkins are shipped within 7 to 10 Business Days after your order is received AND a proof has been approved. 
Shipping takes up to 5 days in US. Please contact us for a shipping quote if you are an international customer. 
IN A RUSH?
Need the napkins sooner than 14 days?  Napkins can be shipped within 24-48 hours (time varies depending on if proof approval is needed and when your order is received) with rush production (40 fee). Expedited shipping can also be purchased at checkout for faster shipping times. Please note that purchasing expedited shipping does NOT increase the production timeframe of 7-10 business days. 
To purchase the rush fee add this listing to your cart WITH the napkin listing: 
http://etsy.me/2kmOpOs
Questions, please contact us!
We use UPS and FedEx for delivery and therefore are unable to ship to PO Boxes.
EXTRA THINGS TO KNOW
These napkins are a soft 3ply. 
Included is one color (although up to 2 colors can be used for an additional fee). 
Recyclable
Made & Printed in the USA
Minimum Order - 50 Napkins
Order as many sets as you may need. A good rule of thumb is a minimum of four napkins per guest for a reception with drinks, appetizers, cake. Allow more if you have more than one bar set up. If you are concerned about having too many, consider not putting the date on them so that you can use the leftovers at your new home!
COLOR INFORMATION
Keep in mind colors may vary slightly from your proof to your delivered product due to browser and monitor settings.
When you place your order, please be sure to place all of the personalization information in the NOTES TO SELLER section at checkout. This includes, color, text, font, date needed by, and any other important details we need to know. Please note we are unable to match conversations to orders, and therefore it is very important to put all of in the notes section. 
If this is a time sensitive order you must put the date needed by and please be advised there may be an additional rush order fee needed, and upgraded shipping cost to ensure your order is delivered in the time frame needed.

Product name: 108 inch classic, simple, plain, sheer, cathedral veil, single tier, wedding veil, bridal veil, diamond white, light ivory, blush veil
Description:
A perfect length veil with just enough drama for your look.
This single tier veil is 108 inches wide and is available in a variety length options to fit your bridal dream look.  It also come sewn onto a metal wire comb wrapped in the same material as the veil. This veil have raw cut edge and round at the bottom, and is made with soft bridal illusion tulle, the same material (sometimes better) as you would find in the bridal salons.  The tulle is very sheer, soft, and light and will be the perfect additional to you bridal look.
Veil shown in picture is 108" long.
You can choose from 4 different types of comb options: plain comb (standard no need for addition purchase, price is as listed), Swarovski White Pearls, Swarovski Cream Pearls, Swarovski Crystals, or clear rhinestone applique. And please note, white pearls are more of an off white color, which would be a better match to light ivory veil, unless you have other cream pearls beading or jewelries.  And the 3rd listed picture has the pearl comb option but with White Pearls.  For rhinestone applique option, you can more options/styles to choose from.  To purchase the different comb options, please click on the links below and purchase it with the veil you want in the same transaction.  Please note, adding pearls, crystals, or applique will add another week to production, so please plan you ordering accordingly.  ALL VEILS COME SEWN ONTO A STANDARD PLAIN COMB.
Plain Comb:
If you want just a plain comb, you can simply purchase this listing as is and the veil will comb sewn to the comb.  No additional purchase necessary unless you want to upgrade to one of the following options.
Add Swarovski Pearls (single row or clustered style):
https://www.etsy.com/listing/497597073/add-clustered-swarovski-pearls-to-your?ref=shop_home_active_1
https://www.etsy.com/listing/54015029/add-clustered-swarovski-pearls-to-your?ref=shop_home_active_21
Add Swarovski Crystals:
https://www.etsy.com/listing/49323726/add-cluster-swarovski-crystals-to-veil?ref=shop_home_active_23
Add Rhinestone Applique:
https://www.etsy.com/listing/241424430/add-clustered-swarovski-pearls-to-your?ref=shop_home_active_1
Not sure which color will match? Here is the listing for samples: Tulle sample: 
www.etsy.com/listing/65452066/sample-of-veil-material
 
Referring to the picture of the different tulle colors (from left to right): 
White: the whitest shade of white, or also known as stark white.
Diamond White:  despite its name, it’s actually a soft white, off white, candlelight white, and natural white tone, and is not the brightest white shade.  This is the 2nd most popular color.  But in some cases, a designer’s dress might be labeled ivory, but it’s actually a diamond white veil that would work the best.
Light Ivory: the most popular shade.  It a bit darker in shade than diamond white, but a lot lighter than ivory.  Many ivory dress today are in this shade, unless you have a true ivory color dress.
Ivory: more of an antique ivory color or for a dress that’s true ivory.  This is a very dark shade of yellow and not a good match for most ivory dresses.  
Please note, all pictures on my site are sent in by brides wearing my creations and are not taking from other sites. 
Special thanks to the beautiful brides for sending their beautiful pictures, and special thanks to photographers at Harvard Photography: www.harvardphotography.com/ (first photo) and  Vitalic Photo (second photo) for the veil with the pearl add-on.

You get three totally versatile rings that you can mix and match with your other stacking rings to make completely different looks,  wear them together or as single rings or put them with some of your other stacking rings. !! Please note. Once a ring is soldered the silver is annealed ( softened) and needs to be tumbled to harden it again. The tumbling removes  patina and makes the ring bright and shiney. Exposure to the elements will cause darkness/ tarnish in the recesses. So your ring will arrive with a bright shiney finish, but as you wear it -it will patina naturally and darken in the recesses. There are ways to speed up this process and I can provide you with that information if requested. The ring will arrive freshly tumbled and not be dark in the recesses- but acquire the look with a little time. The darkness in the photo of the ring in this listing is naturally occuring patina from wear. The photo represents what this ring will look like through the majority of its life - except for a short time after tumbling which is necessary for the ring to retain its round shape.  Light polishing will keep the high points shiney and the recesses dark. !!

Product name: Green Ombre Faceted Gem Statement Necklace
Description:
This green ombre statement necklace adds a bold pop to any outfit! It can easily be worn to dress up a classic top or dress, or simply paired with jeans and a t-shirt.

I strive for integrity in all my shop interactions. Your satisfaction is 100% guaranteed. Please read my shop policies for additional information.
**Important: Unless otherwise noted, all of the findings (ear wires, chains, etc.), framed gems, and charms in the jewelry is plated. Plated findings have a brass core with a thin layer of the metal color, the color that you see, on the outside. This means that it will tarnish (become slightly discolored, or wear out) over time. Plated materials are used to keep prices lower, so jewelry is more affordable for you! In order to keep your jewelry from quickly tarnishing, store jewelry in a closed container, away from other jewelry. It's best to avoid extreme weather and moisture.

Product name: Medical Alert Bracelet, Medical ID Bracelet, Diabetic Bracelet, Medical Bracelet, Allergy Alert Bracelet, Brass Gold Bracelet, Personalized
Description:
This beautiful brass cuff is hand stamped with Caduceus symbol on the front of the bracelet and a medical alert on the inside of the cuff (up to 45 characters). It can be stamped with a medical condition or allergies or anything else that is crucial during a medical emergency. 
Pictured cuff has a brushed finish - simply beautiful.
Second image shows cuff in hammered finish (left) brushed (center) polished finish (right).
Medical symbol can be stamped on the ends as well.
The cuff is 1/4" by 6" and is perfect for stacking. (if fits comfortably up to 7.5 in wrist by adjusting the opening, if you need smaller or larger size please contact me PRIOR to placing an order)
In "message to seller" at checkout, please let me know what you would like stamped on the inside of the bracelet.
Please note that all metals including brass, copper and sterling silver will develop a natural patina over time. You can polish it to shine using a polishing cloth or choose to leave it which gives your price an antiqued look. I apply protective coating but it does wear off over time. If you prefer raw brass so the cuff develops natural patina please let me know.

Description:

How about 'Keep on running', 'Go Dad!', 'Marathon Man' or 'Go Go Go!'
These curved, shiny aluminium charms can be hand-stamped with your chosen message - as long as it fits.

Tell us what message(s) you would like and the font in the Notes to Seller. 
Allow no more 14 characters including spaces - in 2 rows max 7 characters on each. See available fonts in picture. Each pair is made to order, letter placement may vary. Tags are polished and finished with a coat of tough wax.
Thread your aglets through the eyelets!
Now also available in copper and brass. See our other shop listings.
